{
  "id": "RAW_730aa133",
  "title": "WeatherNext 2：我们最先进的天气预测模型",
  "url": "https://blog.google/technology/google-deepmind/weathernext-2/",
  "date": "2025-11-17 15:00:00",
  "author": "The WeatherNext team",
  "siteName": "The Keyword (blog.google) ",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"WeatherNext 2: Our most advanced weather forecasting model\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2025-11-17T15:00:00.703696+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\" data-highlight-mode=\"word-over-paragraph\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <span width=\"14px\"> \n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg> \n    </span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;WeatherNext 2: Our most advanced weather forecasting model&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"ceue8\" class=\"drop-cap\">The weather affects important decisions we make everyday — from global supply chains and flight paths to your daily commute. In recent years, artificial intelligence (AI) has dramatically enhanced what’s possible in weather forecasting and the ways in which we can use it.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"asrg4\">Today, Google DeepMind and Google Research are introducing <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/science/weathernext/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WeatherNext 2</a>, our most advanced and efficient forecasting model. WeatherNext 2 can generate forecasts 8x faster and with resolution up to 1-hour. This breakthrough is enabled by a new model that can provide hundreds of possible scenarios. Using this technology, we’ve supported weather agencies in making decisions based on a range of scenarios through our <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/blog/how-were-supporting-better-tropical-cyclone-prediction-with-ai/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">experimental cyclone predictions</a>.\n      <br></p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"7e6cp\">We're now taking our research out of the lab and putting it into the hands of users. WeatherNext 2's forecast data is now available in <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/earth-engine/datasets/catalog/projects_gcp-public-data-weathernext_assets_weathernext_2_0_0\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Earth Engine</a> and <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/bigquery/analytics-hub/exchanges/projects/871883017250/locations/us/dataExchanges/weathernext_19397e1bcb7/listings/weathernext_2_19a39fe59dd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">BigQuery</a>. We’re also launching an <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/publishers/google/model-garden/weather-next-v2\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">early access program</a> on Google Cloud’s Vertex AI platform for custom model inference.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"46t7n\">By incorporating WeatherNext technology, we’ve now upgraded weather forecasts in Search, Gemini, Pixel Weather and Google Maps Platform’s <a href=\"https://mapsplatform.google.com/maps-products/weather/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Weather API</a>. In the coming weeks, it will also help power weather information in Google Maps.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"2\" thumbnail-alt=\"WeatherNext demo video\" video-id=\"YQwqoEm_xis\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Youtube Video&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"YQwqoEm_xis\" data-index-id=\"2\" data-type=\"video\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n      <button class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/YQwqoEm_xis/default.webp\" alt=\"WeatherNext demo video\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/YQwqoEm_xis/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/YQwqoEm_xis/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"><!----></uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \"><!----></uni-icon-component><!--?lit$578422249$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;WeatherNext 2: Our most advanced weather forecasting model&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"ceue8\">Predicting more possible scenarios</h2>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"Diagram showing the new algorithm used in WeatherNext 2.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"WeatherNext 2: Our most advanced weather forecasting model\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;WeatherNext 2: Our most advanced weather forecasting model&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"Diagram showing the new algorithm used in WeatherNext 2.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WeatherNext_2-blog-figure-03_larg.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WeatherNext_2-blog-figure-03_larg.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WeatherNext_2-blog-figure-03_lar.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <figcaption class=\"image-full-width__caption\">\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <div slot=\"caption-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <div class=\"rich-text\">\n       <p data-block-key=\"bh0mo\">From a single input, we use independently trained neural networks and inject noise in function space to create coherent variability in weather forecast predictions.</p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    </figcaption>\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;WeatherNext 2: Our most advanced weather forecasting model&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"3zlr3\">Weather predictions need to capture the full range of possibilities — including worst case scenarios, which are the most important to plan for.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"6r34e\">WeatherNext 2 can predict hundreds of possible weather outcomes from a single starting point. Each prediction takes less than a minute on a single TPU; it would take hours on a supercomputer using physics-based models.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"gehb\">Our model is also highly skillful and capable of higher-resolution predictions, down to the hour. Overall, WeatherNext 2 surpasses our previous state-of-the-art WeatherNext model on 99.9% of variables (e.g. temperature, wind, humidity) and lead times (0-15 days), enabling more useful and accurate forecasts.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"dsjdl\">This improved performance is enabled by a new AI modelling approach called a <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.10772\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Functional Generative Network</a> (FGN), which injects ‘noise’ directly into the model architecture so the forecasts it generates remain physically realistic and interconnected.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"56vt3\">This approach is particularly useful for predicting what meteorologists refer to as “marginals” and “joints.” Marginals are individual, standalone weather elements: the precise temperature at a specific location, the wind speed at a certain altitude or the humidity. What's novel about our approach is that the model is only trained on these marginals. Yet, from that training, it learns to skillfully forecast 'joints' — large, complex, interconnected systems that depend on how all those individual pieces fit together. This 'joint' forecasting is required for our most useful predictions, such as identifying entire regions affected by high heat, or expected power output across a wind farm.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"Heatmaps showing WeatherNext 2 consistently outperforms WeatherNext Gen across nearly all atmospheric variables, pressure levels, and lead times.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"WeatherNext 2: Our most advanced weather forecasting model\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;WeatherNext 2: Our most advanced weather forecasting model&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"Heatmaps showing WeatherNext 2 consistently outperforms WeatherNext Gen across nearly all atmospheric variables, pressure levels, and lead times.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WeatherNext2vs_graphic.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WeatherNext2vs_graphic.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WeatherNext2vs_graphic.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <figcaption class=\"image-full-width__caption\">\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <div slot=\"caption-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <div class=\"rich-text\">\n       <p data-block-key=\"ondbd\">Continuous Ranked Probability Score (CRPS) comparing WeatherNext 2 to WeatherNext Gen</p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    </figcaption>\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;WeatherNext 2: Our most advanced weather forecasting model&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"3zlr3\">From research to reality</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"7g8gm\">With WeatherNext 2, we're translating cutting edge research into high-impact applications. We’re committed to advancing the state of the art of this technology and making our latest tools available to the global community.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"An animation showing how WeatherNext turns operational inputs into useful applications\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"weathernext 2\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WeatherNext2_figure_03.mp4\" section-header=\"WeatherNext 2: Our most advanced weather forecasting model\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;WeatherNext 2: Our most advanced weather forecasting model&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <video autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"An animation showing how WeatherNext turns operational inputs into useful applications\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WeatherNext2_figure_03.mp4\">\n      Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WeatherNext2_figure_03.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n     </video>\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <!--?lit$578422249$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;WeatherNext 2: Our most advanced weather forecasting model&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"3zlr3\">Looking ahead, we’re actively researching capabilities to improve our models, including integrating new data sources, and expanding access even further. By providing powerful tools and open data, we hope to accelerate scientific discovery and empower a global ecosystem of researchers, developers and businesses to make decisions on today’s most complex problems and build for the future.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"1ulr3\">To learn more about geospatial platforms and AI work at Google, check out <a href=\"http://earth.google.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google Earth</a>, <a href=\"https://earthengine.google.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Earth Engine</a>, <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaearth-foundations-helps-map-our-planet-in-unprecedented-detail/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">AlphaEarth Foundations</a>, and <a href=\"https://ai.google/earth-ai/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Earth AI</a>.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"5vn1t\">Learn more about WeatherNext 2</h2>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"6tpna\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.10772\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Read our paper</a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"akg5j\"><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/weathernext\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WeatherNext developer documentation</a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"7tho1\">Explore the <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/earth-engine/datasets/catalog/projects_gcp-public-data-weathernext_assets_weathernext_2_0_0\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Earth Engine Data Catalog</a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"59krp\">Query forecast data in <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/bigquery/analytics-hub/exchanges/projects/871883017250/locations/us/dataExchanges/weathernext_19397e1bcb7/listings/weathernext_2_19a39fe59dd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">BigQuery</a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"7pgsf\">Sign up to the <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/publishers/google/model-garden/weather-next-v2\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">early access program</a> for Cloud Vertex AI<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-related-content-tout title=\"GenCast predicts weather and the risks of extreme conditions\" cta=\"See more\" summary=\"New AI model advances the prediction of weather uncertainties and risks, delivering faster, more accurate forecasts up to 15 days ahead.\" hideimage=\"False\" eyebrow=\"Google DeepMind Blog\" image-alt-text=\"side by side images of weather and predictions\" role=\"none\" externalurl=\"https://deepmind.google/discover/blog/gencast-predicts-weather-and-the-risks-of-extreme-conditions-with-sota-accuracy/\" fullurl=\"\" pagetype=\"\" isarticlepage=\"\">\n   <!---->\n   <section role=\"none\" class=\" related-content-tout related-content-tout--max-width uni-component-spacing \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Related Content Tout&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;GenCast predicts weather and the risks of extreme conditions&quot;}\">\n    <a class=\"related-content-tout__wrapper\" href=\"https://deepmind.google/discover/blog/gencast-predicts-weather-and-the-risks-of-extreme-conditions-with-sota-accuracy/\" aria-label=\"\n      Google DeepMind Blog.\n      side by side images of weather and predictions. GenCast predicts weather and the risks of extreme conditions.\n      New AI model advances the prediction of weather uncertainties and risks, delivering faster, more accurate forecasts up to 15 days ahead. See more\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><!--?lit$578422249$--></a>\n   </section>\n  </uni-related-content-tout>\n  <uni-related-content-tout title=\"GraphCast\" cta=\"See more\" summary=\"An AI model for faster and more accurate global weather forecasting.\" hideimage=\"False\" eyebrow=\"Google DeepMind Blog\" image-alt-text=\"world map with purple and blue swirls\" role=\"none\" externalurl=\"https://deepmind.google/discover/blog/graphcast-ai-model-for-faster-and-more-accurate-global-weather-forecasting/\" fullurl=\"\" pagetype=\"\" isarticlepage=\"\">\n   <!---->\n   <section role=\"none\" class=\" related-content-tout related-content-tout--max-width uni-component-spacing \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Related Content Tout&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;GraphCast&quot;}\">\n    <a class=\"related-content-tout__wrapper\" href=\"https://deepmind.google/discover/blog/graphcast-ai-model-for-faster-and-more-accurate-global-weather-forecasting/\" aria-label=\"\n      Google DeepMind Blog.\n      world map with purple and blue swirls. GraphCast.\n      An AI model for faster and more accurate global weather forecasting. See more\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><!--?lit$578422249$--></a>\n   </section>\n  </uni-related-content-tout>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google DeepMind 推出 WeatherNext 2，这是一款先进的 AI 模型，用于天气预测，它使用一种新颖的函数式生成网络 (FGN)，提供快 8 倍的速度、更高的分辨率和多情景预测。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google DeepMind 推出 WeatherNext 2，这是一款先进的 AI 模型，用于天气预测，它使用一种新颖的函数式生成网络 (FGN)，提供快 8 倍的速度、更高的分辨率和多情景预测。",
  "summary": "Google DeepMind 和 Google Research 推出了 WeatherNext 2，这是他们最先进和高效的 AI 天气预测模型。这款突破性的模型以快 8 倍的速度生成预测，分辨率高达 1 小时。此外，它还可以从单个输入预测数百种可能的天气情景，而使用传统的基于物理的模型则需要数小时才能完成。WeatherNext 2 利用了一种名为函数式生成网络 (FGN) 的新型 AI 建模方法。FGN 将“噪声”直接注入到模型架构中，确保预测保持物理上的真实性和相互关联性，即使仅在单个“边缘分布”上进行训练，也能出色地预测复杂的“联合分布”。这种能力在 99.9% 的变量和提前期上大大超过了其前身 WeatherNext。Google 正在将 WeatherNext 2 集成到其核心产品中，如搜索、Gemini、Pixel Weather 和 Google Maps Platform 的天气 API。此外，预测数据可通过 Earth Engine、BigQuery 和 Google Cloud 的 Vertex AI 上的早期访问计划提供给开发者和研究人员，旨在加速科学发现并助力全球范围内的数据驱动决策。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "WeatherNext 2 提供更快、更高分辨率的天气预测。",
      "explanation": "该模型以快 8 倍的速度生成预测，分辨率为 1 小时，与之前的模型和传统的基于物理的方法相比，显著提高了预测的及时性和精确性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该模型可以从单个起点预测数百种可能的天气结果。",
      "explanation": "通过提供广泛的连贯且物理上真实的预测可能性，这种能力对于全面规划至关重要，尤其是在应对最坏情况时。"
    },
    {
      "point": "新型函数式生成网络 (FGN) 实现高级“联合分布”预测。",
      "explanation": "FGN 将噪声直接注入到模型架构中，使其能够熟练地从单个天气要素（“边缘分布”）的训练中学习和预测复杂的、相互连接的天气系统（“联合分布”）。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Google 正在使 WeatherNext 2 可以广泛应用和集成。",
      "explanation": "该模型的数据可通过 Earth Engine 和 BigQuery 获得，并通过 Vertex AI 进行自定义推理，并且正在集成到 Google 的关键产品中，从而推广了高级天气情报的应用。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "WeatherNext 2 可以生成快 8 倍的预测，分辨率高达 1 小时。",
    "WeatherNext 2 可以从单个起点预测数百种可能的天气结果。",
    "这种改进的性能得益于一种新的 AI 建模方法，称为函数式生成网络 (FGN)，它将“噪声”直接注入到模型架构中，因此它生成的预测在物理上保持真实且相互关联。",
    "我们的方法的新颖之处在于，该模型仅在这些边缘分布上进行训练。然而，通过这种训练，它可以熟练地预测“联合分布”——大型、复杂、相互连接的系统，这些系统取决于所有这些单独的部分如何组合在一起。"
